description:
Dear MonetDB Developers,

I encountered an unexpected result related to an anti join. If you have the opportunity to take a look, I would greatly appreciate your time and efforts. 
```sql
CREATE TABLE t0(c0 INT, c1 INT);
CREATE TABLE t1(c0 INT);

INSERT INTO t0(c0) VALUES(1);
INSERT INTO t1(c0) VALUES(1);


SELECT t0.c0 FROM t0 WHERE NOT EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM t1 WHERE t0.c1);
-- Wrong Execution Result: empty result
-- Expected Result: 1

```
